	<packaging>jar</packaging>

	<name>SPF portal utilities</name>
	<description>
		Utilities for the portal side of the Shared Portal Framework.
		These are currently based on Vignette Portal. They currently
		include concrete utility classes for portal file interpolation
		(used by the global help secondary page, for example),
		internationalization (including generating localized resource
		file URLs and getting localized message properties with various
		optional hooks such as contextual help), help (including
		contextual and global help), etc.
	</description>

